{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/Store_Page_Text_1.png?t=1737418061\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/Welcome_Gif.gif?t=1737418061\" />Match two identical monsters hiding inside cursed tombstones to score points and unleash powerful monster effects upon your enemy (for example if you match two <strong>Eternal Weavers</strong> you will slow your enemy  speed by 30% for 6 seconds).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Match your monster pairs before your enemy does and get awesome rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/Store_Page_Text_2.png?t=1737418061\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/Modes2.gif?t=1737418061\" />Battle in three game modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* Prove your worth in fast-paced PvP battles against players around the world;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* Conquer the Campaign mode and find unique challenges and rewards within; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* Survive the Roguelike mode and try out new strategies every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/Store_Page_Text_3.png?t=1737418061\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/Monsters_Gif.gif?t=1737418061\" />Find and collect new monsters and unleash  terror on your enemies. Every monster has a unique effects and can become even stronger when you infuse them with a <strong>Dark Pact</strong> charge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are four classes to choose from when picking your monster squad: <strong>Slasher, Curser, Invoker, Alchemist</strong>. Picking the right monsters can enable many possible archetypes such as: <strong>Combo, Speed, Freeze, Ramp, Mismatch, Trap etc</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can collect monsters in a number of ways, through alchemy, digging them up in the Necropolis or as a gift from the Collector. Unlock many customizable options for each monster and alter their appearance: <strong>VFX, SFX, jump scare variations etc</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/Store_Page_Text_4.png?t=1737418061\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/Customize.gif?t=1737418061\" />Find and collect many variations of tombstones, statues, terrains, walls and ambient effects for your graveyard. Design and show off your unique and personal graveyard setup in battles ahead and impress your enemies while you bring their fears upon them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/extras/Store_Page_Text_5.png?t=1737418061\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737418061","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737418061","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/d3a4c6c0bcbcdff1caf6b6d1fc047f29094ba5ce/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737418061","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159350/d3a4c6c0bcbcdff1caf6b6d1fc047f29094ba5ce/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737418061","categories":[{"description":"